Wow. It really sucks to be this guy. Like, really, really sucks. Take your +1, you magnificent beary monster.

To counterpoint what Dr Leonard said above, I think not having the additional characteristics only feeds more fridge horror to this article. This poor guy could be anybody. Young, old, European, Africanwhatever. It works like Spiderman's mask. If you don't know Spiderman is Peter Parker, then all you know is he's a male. He could be anyone. Your brother, cousin, father, the nice baker down the street or that jerk at the gas station that always short-changes you. Not including those details, I think, really adds to the awfulness of this poor sap's existence.







